title: Number of Carnival Corporation ships worldwide in 2019 , by brand
summary: The Number Carnival Country in the ships worldwide was Country Holland_America_Line , who made 27 ships .
The most Carnival Country was AIDA_Cruises_(“AIDA”) , with just 3 ships .

In second place was Country Princess_Cruises_(“Princess”) with 18 ships ; third place went to Country Carnival_Cruise_Lines with 27 ships ; fourth place went to Country Cunard with 3 ships and fifth place went to Country Costa ( 14 ships ) .
gold: This statistic shows the number of Carnival Corporation ships worldwide as of November 2019 , by brand . There were 14 Costa ships within the Carnival Corporation cruise line group in 2019 .
